{"tid":2235102,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"大圍站上蓋商場比青衣城更大","createTime":"2020-10-08T11:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T14:35:58.000Z","uid":101341,"like":11,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a4b7f021af3f353b60e4b2d1bc2d8e86733ef5","tid":2235102,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"新世界旗下大圍站上蓋項目柏傲莊是今年的焦點新盤之一，大圍已經多年沒有新盤推出，而這個區的發展潛力相當高，商場購物與交通配套未來亦會有重大變化，地產站同你一齊了解柏傲莊所在的位置附近未來變化！<br />\n<br />\n大圍一直以來都沒有大型購物商場，居民的衣食住行需要都依賴地舖或舊式商場，例如金禧商場。如欲大型連鎖店或時裝店，最近要到沙田新城市廣場或九龍塘站的又一城。<br />\n<br />\n不過，待大圍站上蓋的商場落成後，相信會大大改變區內居民的消費習慣，大圍站商場提供約65萬平方呎樓面面積，由港鐵全資發展。這個商場更是新界東港鐵商場中最大，比沙田Citylink及火炭駿景廣場大，亦比58萬平方呎的青衣城更大。"},{"pid":"25c596524b6e53c9155ac577f873adc2e4dd2b12","tid":2235102,"uid":176304,"like":125,"dislike":9,"score":116,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"開DONKI OK?"},{"pid":"7a890faeb19a7908912a4492dcb89efd3a6774d5","tid":2235102,"uid":304431,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:50:28.000Z","msg":"有冇咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇落同mikiki差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386d144a67fc54d02be8109812517e00ccc00d49","tid":2235102,"uid":71620,"like":31,"dislike":9,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:51:46.000Z","msg":"青衣城有二期，新城市有三期。大圍站商場可以大過曬佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7433eb149ee18171b16e0e02de1310eef59fabe9","tid":2235102,"uid":125357,"like":207,"dislike":2,"score":205,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:52:20.000Z","msg":"未又係個D舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />